        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "PRAYER INVITES\nGod's Presence to suffuse our spirits,\nGod's will to prevail in our lives.\nPrayer may not bring water to parched fields,\nnor mend a broken bridge,\nnor rebuild a ruined city.\nBut prayer can water an arid soul,\nmend a broken heart,\nrebuild a weakened will.",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-07-13T17:46:28.749Z",
      "creator": {
        "isGuest": true,
        "id": "L50QrGA3RTeSa8pcQLi_"
